      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣はすっごい楽しかったよ？　あ、でも\n麻奈ちゃんが{user}さんのこと……",
      "startTime": 52.0000042597,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "「一緒に買い物に行くと、す～ぐクタクタに\nなっちゃうの」……なんて言ってたかな",
      "startTime": 57.1666709263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
