      "text": "あ、見て！　あのお化け屋敷\nちょうど麻奈ちゃんと遊びに来た時もやってた！",
      "startTime": 114.0333113989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
