      "text": "聞いてもごまかされちゃったんだけど\n麻奈ちゃんとお化け屋敷で、何かあったの？",
      "startTime": 147.9666498185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　ま、まぁ……うん……\nでも、幽霊になってもお化けが怖いって変な話だよな",
      "startTime": 154.9666498185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.9333164852
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-mei018.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、顔赤いよ？",
      "startTime": 159.9333164852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
