    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "き、気の所為じゃないか？\nそういう芽衣は、お化け屋敷、怖くないのか？",
      "startTime": 165.4999678929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-mei019.m4a",
      "text": "う～ん、びっくりしちゃう時はあるかなぁ。幽霊役の\nスタッフさんの後ろに、本物の幽霊がいた時とか",
      "startTime": 173.6666345596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 177.733308347
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-mei020.m4a",
      "text": "どっちに反応すればいいのー！？　ってなって\nわー！　ってなっちゃう！",
      "startTime": 181.0999750137,
